    "text": "Join Healthline and (RED) in the fight against AIDS\nLEARN MORE\nHealthline\nHealth Conditions\nDiscover\nPlan\nConnect\nShop\nSUBSCRIBE\n9 Tips to Navigate Social Media During the Holidays\nYou can turn down the noise of your feed and regain a bit of calm.\nSeason of Self-Care: Gift Guides and More\nYour guide to self-care this holiday season.\nEXPLORE BY\nVIEW ALL\nNutrition\nSleep\nMental Health\nFitness\nProduct Reviews\nTHIS JUST IN\nHow to Be Kind to Yourself During the Holiday Hustle\nHere are 12 ways to set boundaries and gift yourself grace this year.\nHealthline-Approved Celebrity Wellness Picks for Star-Studded Holidays\nThese 13 A-list suggestions can help you spread some red carpet-level cheer.\nMeasles: CDC, WHO Say 40 Million Children at Risk Due to Low Vax Rates\nMeasles is preventable, but low vaccination rates are leading to more cases.\nCan Humans Hibernate?\nGenes from our ancient ancestors may mean that the possibility is within us.\nWant to pump the brakes on skin aging?\nJoin our 7-day challenge to curb signs of aging and glow up the skin you’re in.\nI'M IN\nYour privacy is important to us\nMORE TOP READS\nA Shot in the Arm: Proactive Health Tips for People Turning 50\nMy HIV Diagnosis\nUnderstanding Financial Stress and Tools to Help You Cope\n15 Unique Holiday Foods from Around the World\nHealthline Reviews: Best Meal Kit Subscriptions\nHealthline Reviews: Best Meal Kit Subscriptions\n0 seconds of 18 minutes, 41 seconds\nHEALTH CONDITIONS\nVIEW ALL\nType 2 Diabetes\nInflammatory Bowel Disease\nMultiple Sclerosis\nBreast Cancer\nRheumatoid Arthritis\nPRODUCT REVIEWS\nVIEW ALL\nVitamins & Supplements\nSleep\nMental Health\nNutrition\nCBD\nSPOTLIGHT\nHealthline\nScience and integrity matter to us\nAt Healthline, we set high standards of quality, research, and transparency for what we share, ensuring you have access to nothing but the best. Here's how:\nTo ensure accuracy, each of our 20,000+ articles is reviewed by a medical subject matter expert such as a doctor, nurse, or therapist.\nOur recommendations are current and based on research thanks to our diligent health and medical monitoring standards.\nFeatured brands are reviewed for medical credibility, business practices, and social impact.\nREAD ABOUT OUR PROCESS\nEXPLORE OUR SPONSORED TOPICS\nVIEW ALL\nKnowledge Is Power with Ulcerative Colitis\nKnowledge Is Power with Early Breast Cancer\nMoving Forward with Advanced COPD\nNo Rheum for RA Pain\nGet our wellness newsletter\nFilter out the noise and nurture your inbox with health and wellness advice that’s inclusive and rooted in medical expertise.\nSIGN UP\nYour privacy is important to us\nAbout Us\nContact Us\nTerms of Use\nPrivacy Policy\nPrivacy Settings\nAdvertising Policy\nHealth Topics\nMedical Affairs\nContent Integrity\nNewsletters\nDo Not Sell My Info\n© 2005-2022 Healthline Media a Red Ventures Company. All rights reserved. Our website services, content, and products are for informational purposes only. Healthline Media does not provide medical advice, diagnosis, or treatment. See additional information.\nAboutCareersAdvertise with us\nOUR BRANDS\nHealthline\nMedical News Today\nGreatist\nPsych Central",
